(126,	1,	'2024-01-21 03:47:42',	'2024-01-21 03:47:42',	'<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Review pages</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Read pages as normal, but keep notes about your experience.   Then when you have completed a page leave a comment with your notes.  Here are some ideas of things to note:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Things that were not clear to you as a reader.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Things that seemed particularly helpful to you.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Information that seemed lacking but relevant.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Examples or graphics that would have helped you. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Links to other relevant resources.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'How to contribute to this site',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'115-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2024-01-21 03:47:42',	'2024-01-21 03:47:42',	'',	115,	'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=126',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(127,	1,	'2024-01-23 16:23:30',	'2024-01-23 16:23:30',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a number of freelancing sites that allow both clients (customers) and talent (workers) to connect.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One very general international sites is <a href=\"https://upwork.com\">Upwork</a>.  It has many categories over a wide variety of trades.    However, the process of getting established and finding work can be quite challenging for a number of reasons.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here is a link with <a href=\"https://support.upwork.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016252373-Build-Your-Profile-Essential-Items\">tips on improving your Upwork profile</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you read our page on <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/front-end-web/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"49\">front end web skills</a> then you saw a link to <a href=\"https://www.frontendmentor.io/\">FrontEndMentor</a>.   That site has now added its own Freelance site called <a href=\"https://hiring.frontendmentor.io\">Frontend Mentor Hiring</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Finding work',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'79-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2024-01-23 16:23:30',	'2024-01-23 16:23:30',	'',	79,	'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=127',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(129,	1,	'2024-01-23 16:30:47',	'2024-01-23 16:30:47',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a number of freelancing sites that allow both clients (customers) and talent (workers) to connect.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One very general international sites is <a href=\"https://upwork.com\">Upwork</a>.  It has many categories over a wide variety of trades.    However, the process of getting established and finding work can be quite challenging for a number of reasons.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here is a link with <a href=\"https://support.upwork.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016252373-Build-Your-Profile-Essential-Items\">tips on improving your Upwork profile</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you read our page on <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/front-end-web/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"49\">front end web skills</a> then you saw a link to <a href=\"https://www.frontendmentor.io/\">FrontEndMentor</a>.   That site has now added its own Freelance site called <a href=\"https://hiring.frontendmentor.io\">Frontend Mentor Hiring</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our friends at <a href=\"https://africamupya.com\">Africa MUPYA</a> have a <a href=\"https://africamupya.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Upwork-Tips-Resources-Oct-2023.pdf\">nice page of helpful tips and resource pointers</a> for getting going using Upwork. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Finding work',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'79-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2024-01-23 16:30:47',	'2024-01-23 16:30:47',	'',	79,	'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=129',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(130,	1,	'2024-01-23 16:33:31',	'2024-01-23 16:33:31',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a number of freelancing sites that allow both clients (customers) and talent (workers) to connect.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One very general international sites is <a href=\"https://upwork.com\">Upwork</a>.  It has many categories over a wide variety of trades.    However, the process of getting established and finding work can be quite challenging for a number of reasons.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here is a link with <a href=\"https://support.upwork.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016252373-Build-Your-Profile-Essential-Items\">tips on improving your Upwork profile</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our friends at <a href=\"https://africamupya.com\">Africa M</a>upya have a <a href=\"https://africamupya.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Upwork-Tips-Resources-Oct-2023.pdf\">nice page of helpful tips and resource pointers</a> for getting going using Upwork. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you read our page on <a href=\"https://michaelkentburns.com/index.php/front-end-web/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"49\">front end web skills</a> then you saw a link to <a href=\"https://www.frontendmentor.io/\">FrontEndMentor</a>.   That site has now added its own Freelance site called <a href=\"https://hiring.frontendmentor.io\">Frontend Mentor Hiring</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Finding work',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'79-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2024-01-23 16:33:31',	'2024-01-23 16:33:31',	'',	79,	'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=130',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(131,	1,	'2024-01-23 16:45:52',	'2024-01-23 16:45:52',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Front end, or<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Front-end_web_development\"> front-end web development</a> refers to the skills and technology related to building pages and applications that run in a web browser.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Skills</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a number of skills to learn in order to be a typical web designer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Almost all of them can be learned at a number of mentor sites.  One of which is <a href=\"https://www.frontendmentor.io\">FrontendMentor</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">HTML - Hyper Text Markup Language</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is a rich markup language which can be viewed and coded in a simple text editing program.   It consists of the text to be presented interspersed with HTML markup tags that specify how that text should be displayed.   The filename usually ends in either .htm or .html to indicated that it can be displayed in a web browser.  The HTML markup standards have been around since the beginning of the World Wide Web.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">HTML5</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HTML5 is simply the 5th major revision of the HTML standards that added significant modern features that make some web pages very dynamic. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">CSS - Cascading Style Sheets</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Javascript - A procedural programming language for web pages.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Front end web',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'49-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2024-01-23 16:45:52',	'2024-01-23 16:45:52',	'',	49,	'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=131',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(133,	1,	'2024-01-23 16:50:47',	'2024-01-23 16:50:47',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Front end, or<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Front-end_web_development\"> front-end web development</a> refers to the skills and technology related to building pages and applications that run in a web browser.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Skills</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a number of skills to learn in order to be a typical web designer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Almost all of them can be learned at a number of mentor sites.  One of which is <a href=\"https://www.frontendmentor.io\">FrontendMentor</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">HTML - Hyper Text Markup Language</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML\">HTML</a> is a rich markup language which can be viewed and coded in a simple text editing program.   It consists of the text to be presented interspersed with HTML markup tags that specify how that text should be displayed.   The filename usually ends in either .htm or .html to indicated that it can be displayed in a web browser.  The HTML markup standards have been around since the beginning of the World Wide Web.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">HTML5</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HTML5 is simply the 5th major revision of the HTML standards that added significant modern features that make some web pages very dynamic. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">CSS - Cascading Style Sheets</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CSS is a speciality language for styling text and graphics. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Javascript - A procedural programming language for web pages.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Javascript\">Javascript</a> is a programming language inspired by Java that is meant to run inside a web page.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Front end web',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'49-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2024-01-23 16:50:47',	'2024-01-23 16:50:47',	'',	49,	'https://michaelkentburns.com/?p=133',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
